# Phase 13: Creator Dashboard & Channel Excellence

Empowering creators with deeper analytics, brand customization, and professional content management.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Channel Branding**: Creators will be able to set a specific "Channel Color" and "Banner Image" that overrides the default UI theme on their profile.

## Proposed Changes

### Studio: Advanced Dashboard
#### [MODIFY] [DashboardClient.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/dashboard/DashboardClient.tsx)
- **Real-time Stats**: Display engagement velocity (views per hour).
- **Video Management**: Add "Quick Edit" for titles and tags directly in the list.
- **Audience Insights**: Add a breakdown of subscriber growth over the last 30 days.

### Social: Channel Customization
#### [MODIFY] [profile/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/profile/%5Busername%5D/page.tsx)
- **Branding Engine**: Implement custom banners and color themes.
- **Content Tabs**: Add dedicated tabs for "Videos," "Shorts," and "About."
- **Verification Status**: Display premium/verified status prominently.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Verify "Ambient Mode" glow matches video content.
- Test "Quick Edit" in the Creator Dashboard.
- Confirm custom channel branding (colors/banners) persists on the profile page.
